		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think it's pretty clear apart from the head pins, but since they're differential I guess it doesn't matter. There are only two possibilities though on how to wire them. The logic could also be better.
<br />
<br />I know I have Rob's translation somewhere, if I can find it I'll upload those pages.

		

